    In (10) below, the verb &#8220;halve&#8221; cannot be linked to &#8220;a reduction of 50%&#8221;, since &#8220;a reduction&#8221; is indefinite.
    (10) Argentina said it will ask creditor banks to *halve its foreign debt of $64 billion &#8211; the third-highest in the developing world .
    Argentina aspires to reach *a reduction of 50% in the value of its external debt.
